metadata.name: Underwater
metadata.description:
This photography artwork raises awearness towards to Marine Pollution — A growing problem in today’s world. Our ocean is being flooded with pollution of chemicals and trash.  

Costume designed and crafted by Morchen Liu — Founder of Mochic. The costume features a half armour made out of metal bottle caps and plastic nets, two of the most common trash often found in the ocean. 

Fashion Design - Morchen
Photographer - Morchen
Lighting and effects - Morchen
Model - Violet 

Image size: 3070 x 4737
Mochic (2017)
